  "texts": [
    "Consequently, analyses for causal maps and related representations are predominantly conducted at the graph-level, as illustrated in studies such as (Shahvi et al., 2021; Wang and Giabbanelli, 2023).",
    "In this section, we provide an intuitive and succinct summary of graph-level metrics.",
    "For a comprehensive overview along with equations, we refer the reader to Sec.",
    "3.2 'Structural Analysis' in (Tchupo and Macht, 2022).",
    "The size of the graph is characterized with respect to the number of nodes and number of edges."
  ]
}